# rsync exclude list for the SiteGround deploy. PRODUCTION-CRITICAL.
# Paths listed here are NOT shipped AND are protected from --delete on the server
# (because the workflow never passes --delete-excluded). See CONVENTIONS.md §6.
#
# Do NOT remove web/app/uploads/ or .env: they exist only on the server (media
# library + production credentials). Dropping them here = first deploy wipes them.

.git/
.github/
node_modules/
.env
.env.example
web/app/uploads/
docs/
README.md
.deployignore
.gitignore
.editorconfig
tests/

# --- This repo's local-only files (audit/scratch/support) — never ship to server ---
SOPORTE-WORDPRESS-SSH.md
local/
relevamiento-periodismofederal-local/
backups/
todo
.DS_Store
